insights.title: Test Coverage Below Target (0.0%)
insights.description: Line coverage is below the recommended 80% threshold.
insights.impact: Untested code increases bug risk and reduces confidence in deployments.
insights.recommendation: Focus on testing critical business logic, edge cases, and recent changes. Aim for 80%+ coverage.

insights.title: Branch Coverage Below Target (0.0%)
insights.description: Branch coverage measures how well conditional logic is tested.
insights.impact: Untested branches can hide bugs in error handling and edge cases.
insights.recommendation: Test both success and failure paths. Add tests for error conditions and edge cases.
